{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive and conquer the post-apocalyptic world of Burntime.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original Gameplay: Play through the original game from 1993 with some enhancements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival: Find food, parts to build traps and people to help you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Conquer: Establish camps around all major cities to win the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remastered Visuals: Enjoy enhanced graphics and wide screen support while still being true to its 90s pixel art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remaster Toggles: Prefer the original graphics, or the AMIGA sound track? Change in the options.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the Development</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This remaster was done by a super fan of the original game.<br>It was only possible thanks to the ok by the creators, and the many issue feedback by fellow fans.<br> <br>It is fully reprogrammed from scratch using the original graphics and sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Issue reports and smaller improvement ideas are appreciated on GitHub.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735572902","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269080/page.bg.jpg?t=1735572902","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269080/c39874766dd4cde8a37f6662bb138f76be178a5a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735572902","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269080/c39874766dd4cde8a37f6662bb138f76be178a5a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735572902","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Scr